	Donna Fulton
	06/19/01 11:19 AM
		 
		 To: James D Steffes/NA/Enron@Enron, Christi L Nicolay/HOU/ECT@ECT, Sarah 
Novosel/Corp/Enron@ENRON, Leslie Lawner/NA/Enron@Enron, Rebecca W 
